text:
Friendly staff and patrons, a bit unclear on pricing, almost boarding dishonest. Careful if you’re approached and don’t speak any local language, drinks might get added to your tab whether you know it or not.
Had fun but felt cheated!
Very nice place with a kind lady boss. This place is run by gangster so becareful not to stare at them
Good place to chill and wind down with singing and beering
